    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my reliable ride! It's been such a fantastic car for me\u2014super dependable and still looks great on the road. It\u2019s in solid condition and ready for many more miles of memories. Whether you're heading to work or hitting the highway for a weekend trip, this beauty won't let you down. I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
