      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and tactile feedback. This specimen has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system overhaul, ensuring the chassis maintains its structural integrity under high lateral loads. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings and dampers. It is an analog performance machine with robust mechanical vitals, ready for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
