    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i, finished in a timeless Deep Sea Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable companion and is in excellent mechanical health. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy luster, though in the interest of full disclosure, there are a few minor stone chips on the lower front valance and one small, professionally touched-up scratch near the fuel door. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in Continental tires with approximately 70% tread remaining, though the passenger-side front wheel shows a light amount of curb rash. Inside, the Canberra Beige leather interior is remarkably preserved. The seats are firm and free of rips or heavy bolster wear, and the genuine wood trim remains crack-free. All electronic features\u2014including the panoramic glass sunroof, Harman Kardon surround sound, and the high-resolution navigation system\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the 3.0L TwinPower Turbo engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, with no leaks or warning lights. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent oil service and brake fluid flush performed just 1,000 miles ago. This is a non-smoker vehicle that has been garage-kept and consistently detailed. It represents a fantastic opportunity to own a premium SUV that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
